<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>INC 25 - Impetus Judge Allocation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: left;
        }
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #d4621c;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #5F9DF7;
            color: white;
        }
        .contact p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .login-button {
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #5F9DF7;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>You're Invited to Judge INC 25 - Impetus</h2>
        <p>Dear <%= data.name %>,</p>
        <p>We sincerely appreciate your participation as a Judge for Impetus 2025. Your expertise and insights are crucial in evaluating the <strong>Impetus</strong> projects, as a part of <strong>INC 25</strong>.</p>

        <div class="info-box">
            <p><strong>Event:</strong> Impetus</p>
            <p><strong>Judge ID:</strong> <%= data.judge_id %></p>
            <p><strong>Date & Time Slots:</strong> <span style="color: #d4621c;"><strong><%= data.slots %></strong></span></p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> PICT, Pune</p>
        </div>

        <h3 style="color: #d4621c;">Allocated Projects</h3>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>PID</th>
                    <th>Title</th>
                    <th>Domain</th>
                    <th>Type</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <% data.projects.forEach(function(project) { %>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= project.pid %></td>
                    <td><%= project.title %></td>
                    <td><%= project.domain %></td>
                    <td><%= project.project_type %></td>
                </tr>
                <% }); %>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <p>We also request you to kindly provide your honest feedback after completing the evaluation.</p>

        <h3 style="color: #d4621c;">Important Instruction</h3>
        <div class="info-box">
            <p><strong>For Online Judges:</strong> If you are judging online, you will receive a Google Meet link before the event. Please ensure you have a stable internet connection.</p>
        </div>

        <h3 style="color: #d4621c;">Contact Information</h3>
        <div class="contact">
            <p>Madhura Pawar – <a href="tel:+918806809022">+91 88068 09022</a></p>
            <p>Arpita Bhandari – <a href="tel:+919518799980">+91 95187 99980</a></p>
        </div>

        <p>We are excited to have you on board and look forward to your valuable contributions.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            © PICT INC 2025. All rights reserved | PICT, Pune - 411043 | India
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
